text: Travante António Williams (born July 29, 1993) is a professional basketball player who plays for Sporting CP. Before going to Portugal, Travante played for CC of San Francisco Rams, Adams State Grizzlies and Alaska Nanooks. ==Honours== Oliveirense * Portuguese League: 2017-18, 2018-19 * Portuguese League Cup: 2018-19 * Portuguese Supercup: 2018 ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:American men's basketball players Category:Sporting CP basketball players Category:Small forwards
